Package: OmniSciKit
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Domain Integrated Research Toolbox for Biomedical and Public Health Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ablikim", "Ali", email = "medical_stat@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A unified R meta-package that integrates bioinformatics, Mendelian randomization,
    machine learning, infectious disease modeling, medical statistics, and sample size calculation
    into a consistent interface. It features intelligent dependency management and one-click report
    generation. The package provides comprehensive tools for multi-omics data analysis, causal inference,
    predictive modeling, epidemiological simulation, statistical testing, and power analysis.
